headline: Better Buy: Joby Aviation vs. Southwest Airlines
summary: Joby Aviation continues to make progress toward reimagining urban air travel.  Times like these are when savvy investors who recognize the potential of quality companies are loading up on their stocks, positioning themselves for long-term gains.  Joby Aviation (NYSE: JOBY) and Southwest Airlines (NYSE: LUV) are two such aerospace names that have popped up on investors' radars.

headline: People skills drive experience wins for Southwest, JetBlue, research finds
summary: JetBlue and Delta have invested tens of millions of dollars training staff to be friendly and interactive, while Southwest hires for attitude.
